WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'HoloH' is a Workbench game where the goal is to move coloured
shapes so they fall in a hole that is located in the center of the
play area. The more shapes of the same type that consecutively
fall in the hole, the more points you get...

  Every time you move the shapes in one direction and none of them
fall in the center hole, a new shape will appear at the opposite
edge.

  One important thing to remember: do NOT move shapes of the same
type next to each other, either horizontally or vertically, as
that would end the game.

  Have fun!

